/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ae4e7c4dad1405a3db4fd100a5a5f260f36897","tid":368553,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T17:16:39.000Z","msg":"成班小學雞以為成世loop雙學左膠篤灰大台糾察人鏈鳩做鳩行就可以將得唔到民主嘅責任轉嫁他人，喂，出面有個post講屋企人政治立場，有超過一半連登仔嘅父母都係藍絲奶共人士，如果你怪左膠次次鳩行鳩做前唔該怪左果班藍絲連登仔父母先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62aaf2341443d7890b71e14c696be15951791b5e","tid":368553,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T17:17:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>啱呀 不過出去遊行都唔會成到大事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，上網齋屌左膠鳩行抽下水威力更大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上網講係無用<br />\n出去遊行一樣係無用<br />\n兩樣野無衝突<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，上網齋屌仲高尚d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85bbbc4bff86b1e5280e0430f5ec3f522d2662ca","tid":368553,"uid":44105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T17:50:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5bf0696a3263587d8debffa41ac8f95065c27dd","tid":368553,"uid":37656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T23:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今晚乜事？成班失敗主義撚，鳩做撚全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n遊行完﹐嗰班人又係時間出黎刷存在感﹐FB 嗰班以為自己係 KOL 既中二病仲多"},{"pid":"e7ef060fa9d3ead88efa0499dc1ee7b354de8246","tid":368553,"uid":64806,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T23:54:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今晚乜事？成班失敗主義撚，鳩做撚全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本土派同五毛冇分別"}]}